Introduction

Hyuk is a South Korean singer under Yue Hua Entertainment.

On January 3, 2022, Hyuk was revealed as the seventh and last member of Yue Hua Entertainment's upcoming boy group TEMPEST. He debuted as a member of the group on March 2, 2022, with the release of their first mini album titled "It's ME, It's WE".
